message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with segmentation of organs in medical images using a convolutional neural network, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper focuses on medical imaging and radiotherapy treatment, which could also place it in the medical (cs.MED) sub-category. Finally, the use of neural networks for medical image analysis could also place it in the neuroscience (cs.NEURON) sub-category.
